'''Sarachnis''', the mother of the [[temple spider]]s, is a mid-level boss found in the [[Forthos Dungeon]], in a former burial tomb south of the Spider Den. She can be killed as part of a [[spider]] [[Slayer task]].

Players will need a [[slash weapon]] or a [[knife]] to access the part of the dungeon where Sarachnis is located; run into the south side of the cave to find her lair.

